Introduction

Lee Seoyoung, popularly known as Anne, is the main rapper and vocalist of the Girl Group "GWSN", under The Wave Music. Before debuting, Anne used to appear in various CFs and Music Videos like in Sunny Hill’s "Goodbye to Romance".
